metadata.description:
Produced by Dutchyyy


Using Drums (which I heavily manipulated) & Vocal Stems from @jameecornelia

50%/50% split between Dutchyyy & Jamee Cornelia

BackStory:

Last Year Catalog Works began Hosting Sample Challenges for fun in the Catalog Discord using stems provided by Artists on Catalog. 
These challenges were open to anyone who wanted to participate and we would hold a playback stream in the discord to listen back to all the submissions. 

The Catalog Challenge began w/ Remcycles, then Cumulus Frisbee, then myself (Dutchyyy) After a Brief Hiatus, Catalog revamped the Catalog Challenge and launched the #CatalogCookOff.

001 - Jamie Cornelia
002 - Pauline Herr
003 - Devin Morrison
004 - Dot
005 - Abjo
006 - Low Leaf

End of 2022 the Cook-Off went on another hiatus to be re-vamped into its next evolution and is expected to return soon better than ever.

Artwork by Dutch.
